---
title: Buttery Basil Barramundi with Green Beans Almondine & Mashed Potatoes
description: This delicious fish dish is positively spring-tacular! You’ll sear seasoned barramundi fillets to flaky perfection, drizzle with buttery lemon-basil sauce, and pair with sumptuous sides of garlicky roasted green beans almondine and sour cream-swirled mashed potatoes. A final squeeze of fresh lemon juice adds a burst of bright, tangy flavor.
